  "content": "=\"takeaway-text\">\n        <strong>Context engineering &gt; prompt engineering.</strong><br>\n        <span style=\"color: var(--text-secondary);\">Don't ask AI to be better. Give it the right<br>tools to close the loop.</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"divider\" style=\"margin-top: 32px;\"></div>\n\n  <div style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 24px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 12px;\">\n      Have you used AI to generate visual outputs?\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"font-size: 20px; color: var(--text-muted);\">\n      How do you handle the \"can't see what it built\" problem? &#128071;\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"flex-grow\"></div>\n  <div class=\"author-tag\">Lim Chun Zhe</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-number\">08 / 08</div>\n</div>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n",
